data.text: @Starhound @carrieffisher It almost didn't happen. At first she was only going to do One day only. And I hesitated to buy a photo-op and it sold out within minutes. Luckily a couple weeks before the con she agreed to do a second day and I purchased it immediately.

@ninjasmacks @carrieffisher I will forever be envious of this. You got to meet one of the most influential ladies in my life. Something I never got to do. That is so cool you got to do this and I will also be forever jazzed you got to!
